{"id":"2491","name":"Last Night, Good Night","singer":"初音ミク","description":"中文翻譯轉自：http://www9.atwiki.jp/vocaloidchly/sp/pages/299.html","videoID":"6hlADpxjj0s","lyrics":"\n\n  <div lang=\"ja\" style=\"font-size:1.8em;width:95%;color:#333;text-align:center;padding:10px;\">Last Night, Good Night - <ruby><rb>初音</rb><rt>はつね</rt></ruby><ruby><rb>ミク</rb><rt>みく</rt></ruby></div>\n\n  <div style=\"color:green;font-size:1.3em;width:95%;text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;\">Last Night, Good Night - 初音未來</div>\n\n  <div class=\"line\"></div>\n  <ul>\n\n    <li lang=\"ja\" class=\"li1\"><span class=\"LyricsYomi\" pk=\"103510\" sn=\"0\" st=\"00:00:44.838\">すやすや　<ruby><rb>夢</rb><rt>ゆめ</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>てる　<ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>きみ</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>横顔</rb><rt>よこがお</rt></ruby></span><span class=\"LyricsYomiKana\" pk=\"103510\" style=\"display:none;\">すやすや　ゆめをみてる　きみのよこがお</span></li>\n    <li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"Translate_zh\" pk=\"103510\">香甜柔軟地 看著你正做著美夢的睡顏</span></li>\n\n    <li class=\"line\"></li>\n\n    <li lang=\"ja\" class=\"li1\"><span class=\"LyricsYomi\" pk=\"103511\" sn=\"1\" st=\"00:01:07.638\"><ruby><rb>気付</rb><rt>きづ</rt></ruby>かず　<ruby><rb>零</rb><rt>こぼ</rt></ruby>れた<ruby><rb>涙</rb><rt>なみだ</rt></ruby>　<ruby><rb>頬</rb><rt>ほお</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>伝</rb><rt>つた</rt></ruby>う</span><span class=\"LyricsYomiKana\" pk=\"103511\" style=\"display:none;\">きづかず　こぼれたなみだ　ほおをつたう</span></li>\n    <li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"Translate_zh\" pk=\"103511\">不經意地　我的淚　沿著臉頰飄零落下</span></li>\n\n    <li class=\"line\"></li>\n\n    <li lang=\"ja\" class=\"li1\"><span class=\"LyricsYomi\" pk=\"103512\" sn=\"2\" st=\"00:01:31.917\">せつなの　ときめきを</span><span class=\"LyricsYomiKana\" pk=\"103512\" style=\"display:none;\">せつなの　ときめきを</span></li>\n    <li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"Translate_zh\" pk=\"103512\">那剎那間的悸動</span></li>\n\n    <li class=\"line\"></li>\n\n    <li lang=\"ja\" class=\"li1\"><span class=\"LyricsYomi\" pk=\"103513\" sn=\"3\" st=\"00:01:41.899\">この<ruby><rb>胸</rb><rt>むね</rt></ruby>に　<ruby><rb>隠</rb><rt>かく</rt></ruby>してたの</span><span class=\"LyricsYomiKana\" pk=\"103513\" style=\"display:none;\">このむねに　かくしてたの</span></li>\n    <li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"Translate_zh\" pk=\"103513\">一直隱藏在我的心中</span></li>\n\n    <li class=\"line\"></li>\n\n    <li lang=\"ja\" class=\"li1\"><span class=\"LyricsYomi\" pk=\"103514\" sn=\"4\" st=\"00:01:53.409\">Last night,Good night</span><span class=\"LyricsYomiKana\" pk=\"103514\" style=\"display:none;\">Last night,Good night</span></li>\n    <li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"Translate_zh\" pk=\"103514\"></span></li>\n\n    <li class=\"line\"></li>\n\n    <li lang=\"ja\" class=\"li1\"><span class=\"LyricsYomi\" pk=\"103515\" sn=\"5\" st=\"00:02:15.500\">この<ruby><rb>夜</rb><rt>よる</rt></ruby>　<ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>きみ</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>手</rb><rt>て</rt></ruby></span><span class=\"LyricsYomiKana\" pk=\"103515\" style=\"display:none;\">このよる　きみのて</span></li>\n    <li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"Translate_zh\" pk=\"103515\">這一晚　你的手</span></li>\n\n    <li class=\"line\"></li>\n\n    <li lang=\"ja\" class=\"li1\"><span class=\"LyricsYomi\" pk=\"103516\" sn=\"6\" st=\"00:02:26.800\"><ruby><rb>握</rb><rt>にぎ</rt></ruby>って　<ruby><rb>眠</rb><rt>ねむ</rt></ruby>るよ</span><span class=\"LyricsYomiKana\" pk=\"103516\" style=\"display:none;\">にぎって　ねむるよ</span></li>\n    <li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"Translate_zh\" pk=\"103516\">我會好好握著　再安然入睡</span></li>\n\n    <li class=\"line\"></li>\n\n    <li lang=\"ja\" class=\"li1\"><span class=\"LyricsYomi\" pk=\"103517\" sn=\"7\" st=\"00:02:38.232\">おやすみ</span><span class=\"LyricsYomiKana\" pk=\"103517\" style=\"display:none;\">おやすみ</span></li>\n    <li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"Translate_zh\" pk=\"103517\">祝我好眠</span></li>\n\n    <li class=\"line\"></li>\n\n    <li lang=\"ja\" class=\"li1\"><span class=\"LyricsYomi\" pk=\"103518\" sn=\"8\" st=\"00:03:02.207\"><ruby><rb>素敵</rb><rt>すてき</rt></ruby>な　<ruby><rb>朝</rb><rt>あさ</rt></ruby>をもう<ruby><rb>一度</rb><rt>